        "subject": "=Your enquiry about {{ $json[\"Project Interest\"] }} — Details inside",
        "message": "=<div style=\"font-family:sans-serif;max-width:520px;color:#222\">\n  <p>Namaste <strong>{{ $json[\"Full Name\"] }}</strong>,</p>\n\n  <p>\n    Thank you for your enquiry about \n    <strong>{{ $json[\"Project Interest\"] }}</strong>.\n    We've received your details and our property advisor will call you\n    <strong>within the next 15 minutes</strong>.\n  </p>\n\n  <p>We're preparing the following for you:</p>\n\n  <ul>\n    <li>Floor plans for {{ $json[\" BHK Type\"] }} configurations</li>\n    <li>Current pricing and payment plan details</li>\n    <li>Available inventory matching your budget of {{ $json.Budget }}</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <p>\n    If you have any specific questions before we call,\n    feel free to reply to this email.\n  </p>\n\n  <p style=\"margin-top:24px\">\n    Warm regards,<br>\n    <strong>Property Advisory Team</strong>\n  </p>\n</div>",
