        "message": "=<div style=\"font-family:sans-serif;max-width:520px;color:#222\">   <p>Namaste <strong>{{ $json[\"Full Name\"] }}</strong>,</p>    <p>Thank you for your interest in <strong>{{ $json[\"Project Interest\"] }}</strong>{{ $json[\" BHK Type\"] }}</p>    <p>Based on your preference for <strong></strong>    within a budget of <strong>{{ $json.Budget }}</strong>,    I think we have some excellent options for you.</p>    <p>Our team will reach out within 24 hours to walk you through    the available configurations and answer any questions.</p>    <p>In the meantime, here's what sets this project apart:</p>   <ul>     <li>RERA approved — on-schedule delivery</li>     <li>Prime location with excellent connectivity</li>     <li>Flexible payment plans and home loan assistance</li>   </ul>    <p>Feel free to reply with any questions.</p>    <p style=\"margin-top:24px\">Best regards,<br>   <strong>Property Advisory Team</strong></p> </div>",
